feedWorker

Class FilterFeedObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • feedWorker.FeedObserver
      • feedWorker.FilterFeedObserver

  • public class FilterFeedObserver
extends FeedObserver
    This class represents an implementation of an observer for feeds. This type of observers filters the feed according to a filter stored as an expression tree. Also, this type of observers stores information needed to be printed.
    Author:
    razvan

    • Field Detail

      • stock

        private java.util.TreeMap<java.lang.String,StockData> stock
        A map of stocks from feed. This map contains the name of each stock and information about the stock.

      • expressionFilter

        private ExprNode expressionFilter
        An expression filter that may differ from observer to observer. It is stored as a tree and it is used to filter what feeds should be printed.

        A visitor to cover the expression tree.
